summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed from Robert A. Lyshol and Birgit E. Lyshol, his wife; and Austin Skeisvold and Maia Skeisvold, his wife, doing business as Lyshol and Skeisvold Enterprises to a portion of Block 13 of Brygger's Second Home Addition to the City of Ballard for the Seattle Model City program.
